Whether its supposed to be a bland noodle bowl or a spicy Kung Pao dish, they all taste the exact same.
Other than the lack of variety with taste, the restaurant is great to pick up food from.
Beware of an odor that goes through the airducts and wall from the buisness next door if you are dining in.
